      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready for a reliable ride that's perfect for your daily commute! This car has been a faithful companion on the road and still has plenty of life left to give. While it shows some honest signs of use and age-appropriate wear, it remains a solid, dependable choice for anyone looking for practical transportation at a great value.",
